Extensions:

    - Complex model / model with walking animation
        - Avatar.java

    - Night mode with torch
        - Game.java
            - SetLighting function to update lighting settings between sunlight and torch
            - display function to change background colour depending on the mode

    - Rain (snow) using particle effects
        - RainSystem.java
            - Instance is initialised in Game.java and is drawn when rain is toggled on
        - MathUtil.java
            - Contains the billboard function used in RainSystem
